t with the dynamical timescales for outflows, but not with the\nseparations of emission knots in outflows, indicating that episodic accretion\ncould either trigger or stop collimated large-scale outflows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Jan 2013 21:05:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
